🛒 CommerceBoard Frontend
CommerceBoard is a modern, responsive frontend dashboard built for eCommerce platforms. It provides powerful UI components, charts, and analytics to monitor sales, customers, orders, and more — designed for seamless integration with your backend.

🚀 Features
📊 Interactive analytics dashboard

🛍️ Product and order management interfaces

👥 Customer insights and activity tracking

⚡ Built with performance and responsiveness in mind

🛠️ Tech Stack
Framework: React

UI Library: Tailwind CSS

State Management: Context API

Routing: React Router

Charts: Chart.js 

API Communication: Fetch

